MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This Mapping retains only 6 months of data in the staging table.
MAPPING.NAME: m_STG_ALL_APLL_MF_RAW_RET

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This SQ fetches the distinct CREATE_TIMESTAMP where the data is 6 months old.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_ALL_APLL_MANIFESTS_RAW

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT STG_ALL_APLL_MANIFESTS_RAW.CREATE_TIMESTAMP AS CREATE_TIMESTAMP FROM STAGING. STG_ALL_APLL_MANIFESTS_RAW WHERE TRUNC(CREATE_TIMESTAMP) < ADD_MONTHS(TRUNC(SYSDATE), -6)
